M|json-prompter-video|{
M|json-prompter-video|"concept": "A quiet morning routine scene conveying calm intentionality and personal wellness.",
M|json-prompter-video|"prompt": "Cinematic 4K shot of a person in their early thirties standing at a bright kitchen window, hands wrapped around a ceramic mug, eyes closed. Soft diffused morning light fills the frame from 
M|json-prompter-video|"style": "Cinematic editorial, warm and naturalistic",
M|json-prompter-video|"camera_movement": "Static with subtle rack focus from foreground to subject",
M|json-prompter-video|"lighting": "Soft diffused morning daylight from window left, warm color temperature, no hard shadows",
M|json-prompter-video|"duration": "10s",
M|json-prompter-video|"mood": "Serene, intentional",
M|json-prompter-video|"additional_parameters": {
M|json-prompter-video|"motion_intensity": "low",
M|json-prompter-video|"color_palette": "Warm cream, sage green, soft amber morning light"
M|json-prompter-video|}
M|json-prompter-video|}
M|json-prompter-video|```